data.description: Discover this stucco-finished luxury home with premium features throughout. The downstairs showcases durable hardwood floors, a spacious sitting room with a double-sided fireplace adjacent to a large formal dining room. For those who entertain, there's a discreet full bar area nearby. The bright formal living room connects seamlessly to a kitchen and breakfast space. The kitchen boasts an updated marble island, countertops, and stainless steel appliances. The master suite is updated for comfort with new carpet and tile. Its bathroom includes a full-size steam shower and a jacuzzi tub. The sizable closet offers plenty of storage. Pella French doors in the master lead outside, and a remote-controlled shade adds privacy. The reimagined outdoor area includes lush landscaping with easy-care turn, a sport pool, hot tub, and a combined outdoor living and dining pergola for gatherings. Upstairs, you'll find three bedrooms, each with new carpet and updated en suite bathrooms. Plus, a media room with ample storage space. This home combines comfort, functionality, and style.
